snippet.title: Mario Kart 64 Remade - SM64 Cup
snippet.description:
This video features my custom track distribution on the SM64 cup, also, the first even made custom winningrun award scene for mario kart wii!

the original track for the award winningrun scene can be found on the modpack too and it was made by paratroopa3, stay tunned for updates and the proper release of the modpack!

Tracks were all made by Waltz, i just updated them, you can find all of them on the mario kart wiiki:

SM64 Inside the Ancient Pyramid: https://wiki.tockdom.com/wiki/SM64_Inside_the_Ancient_Pyramid_(Waltz)
SM64 Shifting Sand Land: https://wiki.tockdom.com/wiki/SM64_Shifting_Sand_Land_(Waltz)
SM64 Lethal Lava Land: https://wiki.tockdom.com/wiki/SM64_Lethal_Lava_Land_(Diego_Vapy_%26_Waltz)
SM64 Castle Grounds: https://wiki.tockdom.com/wiki/SM64_Castle_Grounds_(Waltz)

-times-
00:00 SM64 Inside the Ancient Pyramid
02:49 SM64 Shifting Sand Land
06:05 SM64 Lethal Lava Land
10:45 SM64 Castle Grounds
12:21 Award
